Goal:
The purpose of the test is to test out the tensor_mask is being calculated and updated each time we write into convolutionSize and convolutionCtrl registers.

Details:
After each write to one of (or both) the convolutionSize and convolutionCtrl registers, tensor_mask is being read and checked if the read value is correct.
      writeTensorMask(0x3f3f);
      writeConvolutionSize(convolutionSize);
      writeConvCtrl(convolutionCtrl);
      read=readTensorMask();
      
      writeConvolutionSize(convolutionSize2);
      read=readTensorMask();

      writeConvolutionSize(convolutionSize3);
      read=readTensorMask();

      writeConvCtrl(convolutionCtrl2);
      read=readTensorMask();

